
force create-circular-reveal
  mount build, field view-animation-utils
  mount view, field view
  mount center-x, field int
  mount center-y, field int
  mount start-radius, field float
  mount end-radius, field float

  cause call-method
    drive object, share build
    drive method, |createCircularReveal|
    drive factor, share view
    drive factor, share center-x
    drive factor, share center-y
    drive factor, share start-radius
    drive factor, share end-radius
    raise build, field animator
